# Cursor Skills Catalog Maintenance

Keep the skills catalog accurate and discoverable.

## Requirement
- When adding, renaming, moving, or removing files in `.cursor/skills`, update `.cursor/skills/README.md` in the same change.

## Scope
- Applies to `SKILL.md` files and any supporting files under `.cursor/skills`.
